cat << EOF
Binc IMAP is a well designed, modular IMAP server for Maildir. 
Its goals are to be secure, stable, and fast, yet flexible 
and easy to maintain.
For those familiar with qmail-pop3d, this IMAP server will 
be the natural choice. It is invoked similarily and uses 
checkpassword to authenticate.
EOF
